summary: A clothing mod containing 50 re-textured items for male and female vanilla bodies.
descriptionHtml:
Lots of new clothes, no new meshes but some of the them have been re-textured so that they don\'t look like the originals! Take a look at the screenshots and see for yourself.

-=Location=-
Near the Guardian Stones, along the left hand side of the path that leads down to the hunters camp by the water. Free to take. Chest respawns.

-=Items=-
All items have a male/female equivalent.
